      <title>Nvidia 称三星在 AI 内存芯片设计方面面临挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/nvidia-says-samsung-faces-challenges-with-ai-memory-chip-design</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nvidia 公司负责人黄仁勋表示，三星电子在生产用于 AI 系统的新型内存芯片方面遇到了困难，但他相信合作公司能够克服这些挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/nvidia-says-samsung-faces-challenges-with-ai-memory-chip-design</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 01:31:08 GMT</pubDate>
